          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1705677393409-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a small splash of <strong>water</strong> and cook for a further 4 min or until the pork is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has thickened</p><p>Once thickened, pick your <strong>basil</strong> <strong>leaves </strong>from their stems and add to the pan and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Thai-style basil lean pork with green beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
